			"chat": "",
			"unidentified": "",
			"value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Cleric 1, Paladin 1;\n    <strong>Domain:</strong>&nbsp;Community 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, F, DF<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;50 feet<br>\n    <strong>Area:</strong>&nbsp;the caster and all allies within a 50-ft. burst, centered on the caster<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;1 min./level<br>\n    <strong>Power Points/Spell Points Cost:</strong>&nbsp;1<br>\n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;None\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\n<i>Bless </i>fills your allies with courage. Each ally gains a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls and on saving throws against fear effects.\n</p><p><i>Bless </i>counters and dispels <i>bane</i>.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n"
